{"tid":1219593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青馬大橋係咪試過成隻船炒咗埋去","createTime":"2019-06-13T23:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:29:51.000Z","uid":207951,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5a5ed96e3723420d1fde5b0227b014904cb831","tid":1219593,"uid":207951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:33:23.000Z","msg":"馬灣汲水門大橋昨晚發生撞船事故，一艘船疑駛經汲水門大橋下水域時，船上高物碰及橋底，觸動感應器警報。今早有網民拍下大橋損毀情況，有組件明顯斷裂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bp5MiyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbp5MiyO.png&h=ef7d144f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vv3ugkD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvv3ugkD.png&h=8c87314e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相片可見，橋底位置至少有3條鋼條被撞至斷裂，向外彎曲。該橋高度限制為41米。<br />\n<br />\n汲水門大橋昨晚發生大船撞橋墩事件，令青馬大橋全面封閉2小時，來往香港國際機場的陸路交通及機場快線全部暫停，至晚上約10時恢復通車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f366b750d8013d979684d44a66d4a29c50c9c575","tid":1219593,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e18a7ebb3a7ce80175019fe3e5a3b7adc5ebf","tid":1219593,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:34:08.000Z","msg":"海上不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac6f87c37ac67d1eb41c1751d2911fbf8a3b421","tid":1219593,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:36:33.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸船真係小心d好"},{"pid":"03b6401fdb58812d7aa6c837fd7adf7c9e65ebc0","tid":1219593,"uid":207951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"有無巴打行船？"},{"pid":"9f7405fdb3e23d136f359bdfa96703d301178822","tid":1219593,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB